text: Richard Powell (born 9 December 1960) is an Australian rower. He competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Australian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Australia Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Commonwealth Games medallists in rowing Category:Rowers at the 1986 Commonwealth Games Category:Commonwealth Games silver medallists for Australia
